'''Eddie Byrne''' ([[January 31]], [[1910s|1911]]<ref name="This Week! Ep1" /> &ndash; [[August 21]], [[1981]]) was an Irish actor<ref name="Hammer Complete" /> who portrayed [[General]] [[Vanden Huyck Willard|Willard]], the officer greeting [[Leia Skywalker Organa Solo|Leia]] on [[Yavin 4]] in [[Star Wars: Episode IV A New Hope|''Star Wars'': Episode IV ''A New Hope'']].<ref name="EpIV">{{Film|IV}}</ref>

